Pre-liberation China / Jim White and John Service; interviewed by Banning Garrett.
PRA Archive #: KZ0035
Reflections of Jim White and John S. Service on pre-liberation China. The two Americans, a journalist and a foreign service office, were in China in the 1930s and 1940s.
